description:
Please book your ticket directly with One HealthTech Bristol at [https://www.onehealthtech.com/events-1/womens-health-oht-bristol-techie-brekkie](https://www.onehealthtech.com/events-1/womens-health-oht-bristol-techie-brekkie)

Join One HealthTech for a breakfast event to discuss health inequalities in women's health. Ranging from day-to-day issues including menstrual cycles, menopause and child birth to the representation and research (or lack thereof!) of women's diseases and sicknesses.

This is your chance to explore the challenges and opportunities in improving women's health, and connect with others who have an interest in this space.

Expect tea, coffee and plenty of pastries, as well as an exciting talk by our guest speaker.

Look forward to seeing you there!
title: Women's Health OHT Bristol Techie Brekkie (Tickets via link only)
